# Title: Malicious ShellIntel PowerShell Commandlets
# Author: Max Altgelt (Nextron Systems), Tobias Michalski (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2021-08-09
# Level: high
# Description: Detects Commandlet names from ShellIntel exploitation scripts.
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_shellintel_malicious_commandlets.yml

ScriptBlockText IN ("*Invoke-SMBAutoBrute*", "*Invoke-GPOLinks*", "*Invoke-Potato*")